You are helping build Causent, an AI decision intelligence platform for 
product and business leaders.

Stack: Next.js 14 App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Supabase, Vercel, 
Anthropic API, Recharts, TanStack Table.

Key conventions:
- Use Server Components by default; only add 'use client' when required
- All DB access goes through src/lib/supabase.ts
- Prefer named exports for components
- Keep components small and single-purpose
- Environment variables live in .env.local (never commit this file)
- Use TypeScript strictly — no `any` types

When generating components, use Tailwind utility classes. When generating 
API routes, use Next.js Route Handlers in src/app/api/.